com.wx.properties.property

Class ResourceProperty<PropertyType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wx.properties.property.Property<PropertyType>
      • com.wx.properties.property.ResourceProperty<PropertyType>
  • Type Parameters:
    PropertyType - Type of the property to wrap

    public class ResourceProperty<PropertyType>
extends Property<PropertyType>
    This wrapper offers an access to a precise property of a ResourcePage.

    With an instance of this object, the user can get and set a property of a ResourcePage without actually having any direct access to it.
